        <h2>Specify a default service item</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>
                <MadCap:snippetText src="Customers.flsnp" />
            </li>
            <li>Click <span class="ButtonMenuNote">Service Items</span>.</li>
            <li>Click <img src="../Images/MSPManagerIcons/edit.png" style="vertical-align: middle;width: 19px;height: 15px;" class="no_border" /> next to a service item.</li>
            <li>In the <span class="ButtonMenuNote">Service Info</span> area, click <span class="ButtonMenuNote">Default Service Item</span>.</li>
            <li>Click&#160;<span class="ButtonMenuNote">Save Service Item</span>.</li>
        </ol>
    </body>
